"A modern subscription-finder onboarding application built with React, Vite, Tailwind CSS, and Framer Motion. The project features a comprehensive 7-screen onboarding flow designed to guide users through connecting their email, bank account, phone number, and identity verification with a focus on trust and security. The UI implements glassmorphism design patterns with gradient backgrounds, smooth animations, and progressive disclosure. Key components include reusable ConnectionCard components, an animated ProgressIndicator, and individual screen components for each onboarding step. The application uses React Router for navigation, React Hook Form for form validation, and Lucide React for icons. Mock data simulates connection statuses and user information. The design emphasizes visual hierarchy, micro-interactions, and a consistent color scheme using trust-building blues and greens from the curated palette.\\n\\n**Last changes:** Created complete onboarding flow with 7 screens, implemented reusable connection components with glassmorphism effects, added animated progress tracking, and configured routing with smooth transitions between steps."